name: Queenie & Princess Baby Blue Tank Top
description:
Queenie - This fitted woman's boy beater describes perfectly who is the Queen! Bow Down !!! A perfect summer top for the beach, a barbeque or just enjoying the sun !  Done in either Gold Lettering or White Lettering.  You choose the color ink.


Princess - This fitted boy beater sports Gold caligraphy announcing to all of your royalty. Simple, fun and comfortable this top is perfect for hot summer days and warm summer nights !Let everyone know who is next in line to the throne !!!
